# Data Files Guidelines

All site content is managed through TypeScript files in the `src/data` directory:

## Content Structure
- [about.ts](mdc:src/data/about.ts): Personal bio and information
- [contact.ts](mdc:src/data/contact.ts): Social media links and contact info
- [projects.ts](mdc:src/data/projects.ts): Portfolio projects
- [resume/](mdc:src/data/resume/): Education, skills, and work experience

## Type Safety
- All data files must export properly typed interfaces
- Use strict TypeScript checking
- Follow existing type definitions

## Content Guidelines
1. Keep content professional and well-formatted
2. Use markdown for rich text in about.ts
3. Ensure all links are valid and accessible
4. Images referenced in projects should exist in `/public/images/`
5. Dates should follow ISO format (YYYY-MM-DD)